@darklich14 I seen someone say that they tried to do that with feathers in an altoid tin and it exploded. I’m not sure if they had a hole in the tin for the gases to escape or not but now it has me unsure of doing it. 
I have seen videos of people saying they used soup cans stuffed together with a hole punctured at one end and they were using them in a fire and it was ok. 
If you figure anything out, please let me know and I will vice versa
